rss.resources.app.Models

Interface FeedContract

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FeedSourceContract

    public interface FeedContract
extends FeedSourceContract

    ESTG - Escola Superior de Tecnologia e Gestão
    IPP - Instituto Politécnico do Porto
    LEI - Licenciatura em Engenharia Informática
    LSIRC - Licenciatura em Segurança Informática em Redes de Computadores
    PP - Paradigmas de Programação
    2018 / 2019

    Contract representing the Feed content structure. The FeedContract structure encapsulates the data extracted from a feed using the FeedSource. FeedSource represents the Feed data before the data request and FeedItem represents the Feed data after the (successful) request
